name: Magic Peacocks
description: Deep in the mysterious forest, 5555 Magic Peacocks were born with magical powers inside the Virtual Reality game. Also, peacocks choose their partner peahens to lay Golden eggs to grow their flock. Based on golden eggs and a mix of genes next-generation peacocks evolve with new magical powers to survive.  with a collection of 5555 NFT's on Solana Blockchain which are all part of the Virtual Reality game. We are giving back 50% of sales revenue to Peacock NFT Holders to provide continuous income to our community.
